Package: work.tkgstrator.kiouenginebridge
Name: KiouEngineBridge
Version: 0.1.1
Architecture: iphoneos-arm64
Description: KIOU (Shogi) USI engine bridge tweak. Observes the in-game board state (SFEN) and committed moves (USI) and exposes them over a local WebSocket so a host-side bridge can drive a desktop USI engine (YaneuraOu et al.) against the live position; the engine's bestmove is replayed back into the game. Companion tweak to KiouEditor and KiouKifExporter; all three can coexist. For authorized testing only.
Maintainer: NEVER KNOWS BEST
Author: tkgstrator
Section: Tweaks
Depends: mobilesubstrate
